<P>A
COLLECTION
OF
<HI>Novels</HI> and <HI>Tales,</HI>
Written by
That Celebrated WIT of <HI>France,</HI>
THE
Counte&s;s <HI>D'ANOIS.</HI></P>
<P>In TWO VOLUMES.</P>
<P>VOL. I. Containing,
<LIST>
<ITEM>I. The Hi&s;tory of Don GABRIEL.</ITEM>
<ITEM>II. The ROYAL RAM.</ITEM>
