<ITEM>VII. The Story of the YELLOW DWARF.</ITEM>
<ITEM>VIII. The Story of YOUNG-and-HANDSOME.</ITEM>
<ITEM>IX. The Hi&s;tory of the NEW GENTLEMAN-CITIZEN.</ITEM>
