<P>&startq;Alas! my poor little Ape, <HI>&s;aid the Pri$ce&s;s,</HI> thou
ha&s;t lo&s;t thy Life without doing me any Service!&endq;
&startq;That Honour is re&s;erv'd for me, <HI>interrupted the</HI>
