<P>As the Fore&s;t was not far from her Father's Court,
it was not &s;afe for her to &s;tay there long, le&s;t &s;he
&s;hould be known to &s;ome of the Pa&s;&s;engers, there|fore
&s;he made all the ha&s;te &s;he could to get out of
